t; ambiguous ╬╝ on a multi-╬▓ fit throws; Bernoulli information_limited = true; unsupported families throw). Dependency-free (reuses the existing 20-node GH + elementary functions). Deliberately NOT added to `nongaussian_result_payload` (that shape stays family-uniform and heritability-free).",
